column3: "Sour Diesel is one of the few sativa-dom strains that I'd describe as 'perfect' for daytime use, although it can be a little too much closer to bed. I'd best describe it as being good at just "cutting out the crap" that's getting in the way of your productivity, without negatively affecting cognitive function to a significantly negative extent."
